This folder contains sample build script to get your solution building.  Please do the following:

1. Copy this folder(SampleBuild) to the root of your project.
2. Edit Build.proj and populate the section marked populate
3. In the project root create a folder called Drops
4. Run BuildAndPackage
5. If all goes to plan, you should see 3 zip files in the Drops folder.


Please note that the basis of this sample was stolen from https://github.com/sharparchitecture/Who-Can-Help-Me

